snippet.textDisplay:
Liverpool are currently the best team in the world and have been for the last 12 months imo.
Back to back champions league finals winning 2019.
43 league games unbeaten
97 points last season, Would of won any other league season in history if not for
Manchester Cheaty.
17 consecutive league wins twice.
102 premier league points out of 104.
Best stats out of the top 5 European leagues since stats began.
25 wins, 1 draw out 26 = 76 points.
I can go on and on.
Not even Man City were on this ridiculous level! It's simply unbelievable.
Liverpool are the best football team in the world🌍
